Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_disable..._timing_checks(25.10)  timing_disable..._timing_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_bidi_output_timing_checks

Syntax
       timing_disable_bidi_output_timing_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       When  set to false, timing checks on both the input and output sides of
       the bidirectional pin are analyzed.

       When set to true, the software disables timing  checks  on  the  output
       side of bidirectional pins.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

